             thus deposed: This is the Tankard that the Prisoner offer'd to Sale at my Shop in Portsmouth: I examin'd who he was, and how he came by it? My Name, says he, is 
               <persName id="t17251013-44-person277">
                  John 
                  Barry 
               <interp inst="t17251013-44-person277" type="surname" value="Barry"></interp>
